it of 2% on the total power in\nany such feature. We highlight the importance of correcting for secular changes\nin the simulated accretion disk when performing temporal analyses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 May 2008 20:11:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Nov 2008 02:05:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
